This is a clean, correct `.gitignore` for a Python project using FastAPI, VS Code, and OneDrive.

```gitignore
# Python build and cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pdb
*.pkl
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# Virtual environment
venv/
.venv/

# Environment variables / secrets
.env
*.env

# IDE-specific files
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# OneDrive temporary files
*.tmp
~$*

# Logs
*.log

# FastAPI / Uvicorn caches
*.db-journal